def","tid":16082,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"睇下係邊個官接手佢當地間公司囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽大陸哩講嘢真係on9"},{"pid":"e0436923523420dd4ab5760ce8e714cb41cb7c11","tid":16082,"uid":41848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"呢條仆街同啲仔本身已經係老千底，google下佢個名同集團名就知，仲扮撚晒無辜咁屌佢老母<br />\n我屋企人都係受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}